841040864.query:
WITH bpoly AS (
    SELECT
        ST_SetSRID(ST_GeomFromGeoJSON($1), 4326) AS geom
)
SELECT
    DATE_TRUNC('month', c.valid_from) AS month,
    COUNT(*)
FROM
    contributions c,
    bpoly b
WHERE
    ST_Intersects(c.geom, b.geom)
    AND (status_geom_type).status = 'latest'  -- excludes deleted
    AND (tags @> '{"station": "subway"}')
GROUP BY
    month
ORDER BY
    month;
